page.title: 07Couch Green
page.content:
Couch Green is a small estate consisting of 16 houses and six bungalows. The houses are in blocks of four and there are four blocks. There are two fields at Couch Green.The big field and the small field.The big field has a football pitch and a car park.It is about 213metres long and about 123metres wide.The car park is about 61 metres long and 12metres wide.It has got two swings, a climbing frame, a see saw and a small football goal post. At the bottom of this field, is a long log about ten metres long and there is a bench on the other side of the field.
By Myles Smith
